    <item>
      <title>洛杉矶学区陷入困境的学区总监辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/22/us/superintendent-lausd-alberto-carvalho-resigns.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联邦调查局 (FBI) 调查几个月后，阿尔贝托·卡瓦略 (Alberto Carvalho) 于周日辞职。突袭了他的家和办公室。他从迈阿密来到洛杉矶，以提高学生考试成绩而闻名，但也犯过错误。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/22/us/superintendent-lausd-alberto-carvalho-resigns.html</guid>
